#OXYGEN SENSOR ANALAYZER

#This device was designed for one of the prominent componies in Tehran, iran. until now this design is being produced and sold.
This design has entered the market in the field of medical engineering .

#This device complements the oxygen generator in the patient's room and can detect the tempreture , Purity and Flow of the oxygen gas being produced in the room
and then diplay it.
if these parameters go beyond the set limits ,the device will deep.
also these limits of the parameters can be set by useres in the menu of the device.
this device has 4 page. and these limits can be saved in the flash memory to be permanent.

# SENSOR :Ultrasonic Oxygen sensor 
  MCU    : Stm32f0
  DISPLAY: Oled 2.4 inch   //for showing purity , flow and temprature of the oxygen 
  ALARM  : Active buzzer      //with pwm 
  POWER  : Battery base

# Optimized power and micro memory consumption
# ADC , INTERRUPT , TIMERS , SPI ,UART
# Industrial device manufactured in the Iranian market
##############
#Firmware source code and detailed hardware design files are intentionally omitted to protect intellectual property. This repository focuses on the engineering design process and project outcomes
